						<summary>

						<p>This consists of a few disconnected pieces of writing, of which the first begins with introduction <hi rend="italic">Tirumaṉṉi vaḷara</hi> etc., of Rājēndra-Chōḷa's records and seems to register a gift of land to the temple by one Uyyapirān-Bhaṭṭan.</p>						

