<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<!--<h4>Piece 1</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> tirumaṉ
<lb n="2"/>ṉi vaḷara Iruṉilamaṭantai
</p>

<!--<h4>Piece 2</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">jentra</hi>coḻavaḷanā
<lb n="2"/>ṇa<supplied reason="omitted">t</supplied>tāruḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrīmūla</hi>
<lb n="3"/><hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> Arumoḻi<hi rend="grantha">le</hi>
<lb n="4"/>vatikku
<lb n="5"/>ṇṇāṟṟu <unclear>Uṭ</unclear>tiruttu
<lb n="6"/>patinaṟucāṇ ko
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> Eḻumuḷūr mu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/>vārip poṟṟivaṇniru
<lb n="9"/><hi rend="grantha"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> sahiraṇya</hi>
</p>

<!--<h4>Piece 3</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>ḻatevice
<lb n="2"/>kaiyyeḻuttu Ivvūriya
<lb n="3"/>māvatu Ivvūr <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kātā
<lb n="4"/>kkālukku vaṭakku
<lb n="5"/><hi rend="grantha">t</hi>tu tenkiḻakkaṭai
<lb n="6"/>maṭucca tevak kaṇappe
<lb n="7" break="no"/>vaṅkan ṉuyyapirān <hi rend="grantha">bha</hi>
<lb n="8"/>naṟai <hi rend="grantha">śo</hi>mi<hi rend="grantha">śvarabha</hi>ṭṭa
<lb n="9"/>Epperppaṭṭa Iṟaiyum
<lb n="10"/>Itu <hi rend="grantha">panmāheśvara rakṣai</hi>
</p>

<!--<h4>Piece 4</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>Āka kuḻi
<lb n="2"/>nāna
<lb n="3"/>ya koḷkaiyum
<lb n="4"/>ḷiṭai vilai
<lb n="5"/><hi rend="grantha">m(ā)h<unclear>ā</unclear>sabhai</hi>
</p>

<p>Two more pieces are quite fragmentary.</p> 

